Question: Are there brown desks or dressers?

Reference Answer: yes

Image path: ./sampled_GQA/n23181.jpg

Program:

```
BOX0=LOC(image=IMAGE,object='desk')
IMAGE0=CROP(image=IMAGE,box=BOX0)
ANSWER0=VQA(image=IMAGE0,question='What color is the desk?')
ANSWER1=EVAL(expr="'yes' if {ANSWER0} == 'brown' else 'no'")
BOX1=LOC(image=IMAGE,object='dresser')
IMAGE1=CROP(image=IMAGE,box=BOX1)
ANSWER2=VQA(image=IMAGE1,question='What color is the dresser?')
ANSWER3=EVAL(expr="'yes' if {ANSWER2} == 'brown' else 'no'")
ANSWER4=EVAL(expr="'yes' if {ANSWER1} == 'yes' or {ANSWER3} == 'yes' else 'no'")
FINAL_RESULT=RESULT(var=ANSWER4)
```
